'''Rita Oldroyd''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.

==Bridge accomplishments==

===Wins===


===Runners-up===

* [[Venice Cup]] (1) 1976 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[World Team Olympiad|World Olympiad Womens Teams Championship]] (1) 1976

* [[Gold Cup (bridge)|Gold Cup]] (2) 1967, 1973 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (2)
** 0 (2) 1967, 1973 

